<TEXT>
<P>
Touchstone Announces Another Baby: The baby may be bigger, but the three men 
will be the same in the upcoming sequel to the successful 1987 comedy "Three 
Men and a Baby." 
</P>
<P>
Touchstone Pictures announced this week that sequel "Three Men and a Little 
Lady" will star Tom Selleck, Steve Guttenberg and Ted Danson as the bachelor 
dads. The baby has aged to 5. The director will be Emile Ardolino, known for 
"Dirty Dancing." The movie should be out the end of the year. BETH KLEID 
