<HEADLINE>
<P>
BUSINESS SHOWCASE TO BE HELD FEB. 28 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
ORANGE 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Business Development Committee of the Orange Chamber of Commerce will 
sponsor a Business Showcase from 5 to 8 p.m. Feb. 28 at the Doubletree Hotel in 
Orange. 
</P>
<P>
The event, which will be held in conjunction with the February Business After 
Hours mixer, is designed to let people acquaint themselves with products and 
services offered in Orange County. 
</P>
<P>
Information on becoming a chamber member will be available at the event, which 
will be open to the public. Cost is $5. For more information, call the Chamber 
office at (714) 538-3581. 
</P>
</TEXT>
