Ivana) with, . . . MINDY SCHAUER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, . . . from left, 
Catherine Oxenberg, Georgette Mosbacher, Peggy Fleming, Carolyne Roehm and, 
most recently, Marla Maples, bottom left. ; Photo, Donald Trump ; Photo, Ivana 
Trump 
</P>
