<P>
ANDREOTTI TO VISIT U.S. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WASHINGTON 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Italian Prime Minister Giulio Andreotti has accepted an invitation from 
President Bush and will make an official visit to Washington March 5-8, it was 
announced Wednesday. Bush will meet with Andreotti on March 6 and host a dinner 
in his honor that night. 
</P>
