<DATELINE>
<P>
SACRAMENTO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
No one picked all six numbers correctly in Wednesday night's Lotto 6/49 game, 
boosting the jackpot for this weekend's drawing to a projected $31 million. 
</P>
<P>
The numbers drawn in Wednesday night's Lotto 6/49 game were 16, 18, 20, 33, 42 
and 49 with the bonus number 8. 
</P>
<P>
Twelve people selected five of six plus the bonus number, each winning 
$189,811. Another 346 gamblers picked five of six to each win $3,391. 
</P>
<P>
Sales for Wednesday's game were $21.3 million. 
</P>
